have a new user that signs up

00:30:56.490 --> 00:30:59.650
or an existing user that renews,
we'll send you a message,

00:30:59.650 --> 00:31:01.510
and you now know
you need to continue

00:31:01.510 --> 00:31:03.230
or you need to grant
a new entitlement

00:31:03.230 --> 00:31:07.150
or continue to grant an
entitlement to that user.

00:31:07.150 --> 00:31:10.810
