and implemented account hold--

00:31:10.810 --> 00:31:13.570
and by the way, in case you
weren't looking in that video,

00:31:13.570 --> 00:31:16.600
you really, really should
integrate with account hold.

00:31:16.600 --> 00:31:20.050
We now send you a real
time developer notification

00:31:20.050 --> 00:31:23.140
when the user has a payment
issue and goes on hold

00:31:23.140 --> 00:31:25.390
or when the user recovers
from their payment issue

00:31:25.390 --> 00:31:27.280
and they come off hold.

00:31:27.280 --> 00:31:29.500
So now, immediately,
you will know

00:31:29.500 --> 00:31:33.070
when to withhold entitlement
or to grant back entitlement

00:31:33.070 --> 00:31:34.720
to that user.

00:31:34.720 --> 00:31:37.720
