or other mobile platforms.

00:31:46.990 --> 00:31:48.760
Real time developer
notifications

00:31:48.760 --> 00:31:51.700
also tell you about
voluntary cancellation, where

00:31:51.700 --> 00:31:53.890
the user chooses to cancel.

00:31:53.890 --> 00:31:56.770
In this situation, when
you get that message,

00:31:56.770 --> 00:31:59.960
